<body>
    {{#if product}}
    <!-- ========================= SECTION CONTENT ========================= -->
    <section class="section-content bg-white padding-y">
    {{!-- <section class="section-content padding-y"> --}}
        <div class="container">

            <div class=" container">
            
                <nav aria-label="breadcrumb">
                    <ol class="breadcrumb">
                        <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="/">Home</a></li>
            
                        <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="#" onclick="history.back()">Products</a></li>
            
                        <li class="breadcrumb-item active" aria-current="page">{{product.name}}</li>
                    </ol>
                </nav>

            <br>
            
            <!-- ============================ ITEM DETAIL ======================== -->
            <div class="row product-item">
                <aside class="col-md-5">
                    <div class="card">
                        <article class="gallery-wrap">
                            <div class="img-big-wrap">
                                <a href="{{posterURL}}" data-title="{{title}}" data-toggle="lightbox">
                                    <img src="{{product.posterURL}}" alt="Poster"
                                        onerror="this.src='/img/no-image.jpg'">
                                </a>
                            </div> <!-- slider-product.// -->
                            <!-- <div class="thumbs-wrap">
                                <a href="#" class="item-thumb"> <img src="images/items/15.jpg"></a>
                                <a href="#" class="item-thumb"> <img src="images/items/15-1.jpg"></a>
                            </div> slider-nav.// -->
                        </article> <!-- gallery-wrap .end// -->
                    </div> <!-- card.// -->
                </aside>
                <main class="col-md-7">
                    <article class="product-info-aside">

                        <h2 class="title mt-3 productName">{{product.name}}</h2>

                        <div class="rating-wrap mb-2">
                            <ul class="rating-stars">
                                <li style="width:100%" class="stars-active">
                                    <i class="fa fa-star"></i> <i class="fa fa-star"></i>
                                    <i class="fa fa-star"></i> <i class="fa fa-star"></i>
                                    <i class="fa fa-star"></i>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <i class="fa fa-star"></i> <i class="fa fa-star"></i>
                                    <i class="fa fa-star"></i> <i class="fa fa-star"></i>
                                    <i class="fa fa-star"></i>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                            <div class="label-rating">5/5</div>
                            <small class="label-rating text-muted">132 reviews</small>
                        </div> <!-- rating-wrap.// -->

                        <div class="price-wrap">
                            <var class="price h4">$<span class="priceValue">{{product.price}}</span></var>
                            <br>
                            <h7> {{product.weight}}g <small class="text-muted">(Per Pack)</small></h7>
                        </div> <!-- price-wrap.// -->

                        <hr>

                        <h7 class="mb-3">
                            <span class="tag"> <i class="fa fa-check"></i> Free Return</span>
                            <span class="tag"><i class="far fa-clock"></i> Next Day Delivery</span>
                            <span class="tag text-danger font-weight-bold"> HIT ITEM </span>
                        </h7>
                        <br>
                        <br>
                        <h7>
                            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nulla ultrices dictum pellentesque. 
                            Pellentesque habitant morbi tristique senectus et netus et malesuada fames ac turpis egestas. Mauris luctus tristique ex, et euismod libero pharetra vitae. 
                            Integer vel sodales est, quis rhoncus elit. Praesent ut vehicula massa. Nulla eu eros suscipit, viverra velit at, varius quam. Phasellus nec ligula sit amet tellus viverra laoreet. 
                            Vestibulum sit amet dolor eu est varius sollicitudin at nec odio. Pellentesque mollis risus vel laoreet egestas. Suspendisse potenti. Nunc nec sollicitudin arcu.
                        </h7>

                        <hr>

                        <dl class="row">
                            <dt class="col-sm-3">Delivery time</dt>
                            <dd class="col-sm-9">3-4 days</dd>
                            <dt class="col-sm-3">Availabilty</dt>
                            <dd class="col-sm-9">
                                {{product.stock}}
                            </dd>
                            <dt class="col-sm-3">Typically good for</dt>
                            <dd class="col-sm-9">{{spaceCommas product.category}}</dd>
                        </dl>

                        <div class="form-row  mt-4">
                            <!-- col.// -->
                            
                            <div>
                                <div>
                                    <form action="" method="post">
                                    <button id="btnSubmit" type="submit" class="btn btn-outline-danger addToCart">
                                    <i class="fa fa-cart-plus"></i> Add to cart
                                    </button>
                                    </form>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            
                        </div> <!-- row.// -->
                    </article> <!-- product-info-aside .// -->
                </main> <!-- col.// -->
            </div> <!-- row.// -->
            <!-- ================ ITEM DETAIL END .// ================= -->
        </div> <!-- container .//  -->

        <br>

        <div class="container">
        
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col">
                    <h5 class="title-description">Note:</h5>
                    <h7p>
                        It is recommended to store your herbs in a cool, dry place that is out of direct sunlight. 
                        You may observe some discoloration over time but the product is still completely save to consume. 
                        You may find the manufacturing date and expiry date on the packaging.
                    </h7>
                </div> <!-- col.// -->
            </div> <!-- box.// -->
        </div> <!-- row.// -->
    </section>
    <!-- ========================= SECTION CONTENT END// ========================= -->
    {{else}}
    <h3>No products created</h3>
    {{/if}}
    <br>
</body>
